    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="配置Powerline到WSL上-Ubuntu-18-04"><a href="#配置Powerline到WSL上-Ubuntu-18-04" class="headerlink" title="配置Powerline到WSL上(Ubuntu 18.04)"></a>配置Powerline到WSL上(Ubuntu 18.04)</h1><p>前言：因vim打开注释每一行都看不清楚，就想换配色方案，发现了powerline，但实际上默认theme在vim里的注释也看不清楚�。最后<br>了powerline还调了背景颜色,但是发现o总有颜色的t字是看不清的。。。。。。还是没开tmux的wsl-terminal好用。</p><p>powerline introduction：a statusline plugin for vim, and provides statuslines and prompts for several other applications, including zsh, bash, tmux, IPython, Awesome and Qtile. （我的理解是vim、bash、zsh等的状态栏插件）</p><p>GitHub address:<a href="https://github.com/powerline/powerline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/powerline/powerline</a></p><p>Docs:<a href="https://powerline.readthedocs.io/en/latest/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://powerline.readthedocs.io/en/latest/</a></p><h2 id="安装步骤"><a href="#安装步骤" class="headerlink" title="安装步骤"></a>安装步骤</h2><h3 id="1、前期准备"><a href="#1、前期准备" class="headerlink" title="1、前期准备"></a>1、前期准备</h3><p>由于命名冲突，powerline只能通过python包进行管理。</p><p>因此首先需要安装python环境和pip工具，2和3皆可。我安装的是3，因此以python3.6为例。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、下载安装Powerline"><a href="#2、下载安装Powerline" class="headerlink" title="2、下载安装Powerline"></a>2、下载安装Powerline</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install powerline-status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="安装字体"><a href="#安装字体" class="headerlink" title="安装字体"></a>安装字体</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#通过命令下载字体及配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">wget https://github.com/powerline/powerline/raw/develop/font/PowerlineSymbols.otf</span><br><span class="line">wget https://github.com/powerline/powerline/raw/develop/font/10-powerline-symbols.conf</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#将otf文件移动到有效的字体路径</span></span><br><span class="line">mv PowerlineSysbols.otf ~/.<span class="built_in">local</span>/share/fonts/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#更新字体缓存</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">fc</span>-cache -vf ~/.<span class="built_in">local</span>/share/fonts</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#安装字体配置文件，新一些版本目录为~/.config/fontconfig/conf.d,否则为~/.fonts.conf.d/。</span></span><br><span class="line">mv 10-powerline-symbols.conf ~/.config/fontconfig/conf.d/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、配置powerline到bash"><a href="#3、配置powerline到bash" class="headerlink" title="3、配置powerline到bash"></a>3、配置powerline到bash</h3><p>之后通过pip3的show命令确定poweline的位置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 show powerline-status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>反馈结果示例：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Name: powerline-status</span><br><span class="line">Version: 2.7</span><br><span class="line">Summary: The ultimate statusline/prompt utility.</span><br><span class="line">Home-page: https://github.com/powerline/powerline</span><br><span class="line">Author: Kim Silkebaekken</span><br><span class="line">Author-email: kim.silkebaekken+vim@gmail.com</span><br><span class="line">License: MIT</span><br><span class="line">Location: /home/arsrid/.<span class="built_in">local</span>/lib/python3.6/site-packages</span><br><span class="line">Requires:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>根据你所看到的Location路径在~/.bashrc文件中配置如下</strong></p><p>（即’.’号后面的路径是通过poweline的位置往子目录下设置的）</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">powerline-daemon -q</span><br><span class="line">POWERLINE_BASH_CONTINUATION=1</span><br><span class="line">POWERLINE_BASH_SELECT=1</span><br><span class="line">. /home/arsrid/.local/lib/python3.6/site-packages/powerline/bindin</span><br><span class="line">gs/bash/powerline.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使配置文件生效</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此则配置完毕。</p><p>若出现“powerline/bindings/bash/../../../scripts/powerline-config:: No such file or directory”的报错，需要添加相应的环境变量。</p><p>文档中截图如下</p><p><img src="pic\Install-Powerline-on-my-WSL\0.png" alt=""></p><p>也可尝试通过ln命令的添加软链接解决。</p><h3 id="4、配置powerline到vim"><a href="#4、配置powerline到vim" class="headerlink" title="4、配置powerline到vim"></a>4、配置powerline到vim</h3><p>在~/.vimrc文件中加入如下代码。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">set rtp+=/home/arsrid/.local/lib/python4.6/site-packages/powerline/bindings/vim</span><br><span class="line">set laststatus=2</span><br><span class="line">set t_Co=256</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
